[White "1.d4 d5 2.Nf3 Nf6 3.Bf4"]
[Black "Black vs. London: 3.Bf4 c5 with 5.Nbd2 Bf5 6.Bb5"]
[Result "*"]

1. d4 d5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. Bf4 c5 4. e3
